metadata.description:
Stanford Class of 2022 NFT. 

This is a Stanford supported, student-led pilot project. This project is sponsored by the Stanford Alumni Association and multiple other Stanford entities are involved such as the Stanford Office of Student Engagement.

Carbon offsets have been purchased for all carbon produced through this project.

This NFT is non-transferrable and For Personal Use Only.

Creators: Blake Sharp, Elianna Knight, Viva Donohoe, Nicolas Machado
